  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A non-profit study designed with the aim of analysing the phenotype and molecular
      characteristics (central review) and evaluating prospectively the role of PET-scans in the
      management of primary mediastinal lymphoma treated with conventional approaches.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
